@startuml

[*] --> Idle

Idle : entry / To action
Idle : do / Remain in same state
Idle : exit / Login / Register

Idle --> Register : register
Idle --> Login : login

Register : entry / Register
Register : do / Register after validating
Register : exit / Login / Invalid registration

Register --> Login : valid registration
Register --> InvalidRegistration : invalid registration

InvalidRegistration : entry / Invalid registration
InvalidRegistration : do / Cannot register
InvalidRegistration : exit / Abnormal termination
InvalidRegistration --> [*]

Login : entry / Login
Login : do / Login using valid username and password
Login : exit / Invalid login / To home page

Login --> Home : to home page
Login --> InvalidLogin : invalid login

InvalidLogin : entry / Invalid login
InvalidLogin : do / Cannot login
InvalidLogin : exit / Abnormal termination
InvalidLogin --> [*]

' ---- Home hub (central junction in the diagram) ----
Home : entry / To home page
Home : do / View / Select service
Home : exit / Navigate

Home --> ReadBlog : read blog
Home --> ViewInfectedCount : view number of infected
Home --> ViewDeathsCount : view number of deaths
Home --> UpdateInfectedCount : update current no. of infected people
Home --> ViewMaskDemand : view mask demand
Home --> StockUp : stock up essentials
Home --> SendPatientInfo : send patient info
Home --> ViewPatientInfo : view patient info
Home --> ListMedicalShops : list all medical shops
Home --> AssignCorporationWorker : assign corporation worker
Home --> UpdateCleanlinessStatus : update status of cleanliness
Home --> Logout : logout

ReadBlog : entry / To home page
ReadBlog : do / Read blogs of recovered patients
ReadBlog : exit / Idle
ReadBlog --> Home : back

ViewInfectedCount : entry / View
ViewInfectedCount : do / View number of infected people in the locality
ViewInfectedCount : exit / Idle
ViewInfectedCount --> Home : back

ViewDeathsCount : entry / View
ViewDeathsCount : do / View no. of deaths in the locality
ViewDeathsCount : exit / Idle
ViewDeathsCount --> Home : back

UpdateInfectedCount : entry / To home page
UpdateInfectedCount : do / Update current no. of infected people in the locality
UpdateInfectedCount : exit / View
UpdateInfectedCount --> Home : back

ViewMaskDemand : entry / View
ViewMaskDemand : do / View mask demand in the locality
ViewMaskDemand : exit / Stock
ViewMaskDemand --> StockUp : proceed

StockUp : entry / Stock
StockUp : do / Stock up masks and gloves by the shops
StockUp : exit / End
StockUp --> Home : back

SendPatientInfo : entry / To home page
SendPatientInfo : do / Update data by home quarantined patients
SendPatientInfo : exit / View patient info
SendPatientInfo --> ViewPatientInfo : view

ViewPatientInfo : entry / View patient info
ViewPatientInfo : do / View patient info by the medical professional
ViewPatientInfo : exit / Prescribe
ViewPatientInfo --> PrescribeMedicines : prescribe

PrescribeMedicines : entry / Prescribe
PrescribeMedicines : do / Prescribe medicines if needed
PrescribeMedicines : exit / View data from doc
PrescribeMedicines --> ViewDoctorData : view data

ViewDoctorData : entry / View data shared by doctor
ViewDoctorData : do / View data shared by doctor
ViewDoctorData : exit / Buy medicines
ViewDoctorData --> BuyMedicines : buy

ListMedicalShops : entry / To home page
ListMedicalShops : do / List all medical shops in the locality
ListMedicalShops : exit / Buy medicines
ListMedicalShops --> BuyMedicines : buy

BuyMedicines : entry / Buy medicines
BuyMedicines : do / Buy medicines if needed
BuyMedicines : exit / End
BuyMedicines --> Home : back

AssignCorporationWorker : entry / To home page
AssignCorporationWorker : do / Assign workers to disinfect in an area
AssignCorporationWorker : exit / Update status
AssignCorporationWorker --> UpdateCleanlinessStatus : update

UpdateCleanlinessStatus : entry / Update status
UpdateCleanlinessStatus : do / Update status of cleanliness in the locality
UpdateCleanlinessStatus : exit / End
UpdateCleanlinessStatus --> Home : back

Logout : entry / Wants to leave the site
Logout : do / The session of logged in user ended
Logout : exit / Leave the site
Logout --> [*]

@enduml